NAME RAM Count 1 To 5
DESCRIPTION Stores values 1..5 into RAM module 1 addresses 0..4, then halts.

# Constants
WORD 0 0x1
WORD 1 0x2
WORD 2 0x3
WORD 3 0x4
WORD 4 0x5

# Program
INSTR 40 LDA R0 M0 0
INSTR 39 STA R0 M1 0
INSTR 38 LDA R0 M0 1
INSTR 37 STA R0 M1 1
INSTR 36 LDA R0 M0 2
INSTR 35 STA R0 M1 2
INSTR 34 LDA R0 M0 3
INSTR 33 STA R0 M1 3
INSTR 32 LDA R0 M0 4
INSTR 31 STA R0 M1 4
INSTR 30 HLT R0 R0 R0
